page.title: 17Homes
page.content: {GEORGEHAM} There have been 4 new estates built in Georgeham in the last 15 years and there is one being built now thats Williamson Close.That will have 8 houses on it and because they will be new houses with all the new technology the builders can afford to build them on a very steep hill.Davids Hill is aiso on quite a steep hill and over looks Wiliamson Close.Davids Hill is the biggest estate in Georgeham with 48 houses.The smallest estate is an estate along Chaple Street with 4 houses on it .The other two estates are Putsborough close with 10 houses and Longland Lane with 26 houses both of these estates are on flat ground but out of the new estates they are oldest.There are now more new houses in Georgeham than old.
